<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interface de Vote - Premium Light</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            /* Palette Jaune Fonc√© / Ambre */
            --primary: #c27803; /* Ambre profond */
            --primary-hover: #a16207;
            --primary-light: #fef3c7;
            
            /* Couleurs de fond et texte */
            --bg-page: #f4f6f8;
            --bg-card: #ffffff;
            --text-dark: #1f2937;
            --text-muted: #6b7280;
            --border-color: #e5e7eb;
            
            /* Structure */
            --shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
            --radius: 16px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-page);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* --- EN-T√äTE --- */
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            border-left: 8px solid var(--primary);
        }

        .header-info h1 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .header-info p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .total-badge {
            text-align: center;
            background: var(--primary-light);
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .total-badge span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .total-badge strong {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* --- SECTIONS --- */
        .grid-layout {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .main-content, .sidebar-content {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 25px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        /* --- TABLEAU STYLIS√â --- */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        th {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 12px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bg-page);
        }

        td {
            padding: 15px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bg-page);
        }

        .candidate-cell {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .rank {
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary);
            width: 25px;
        }

        .leader-tag {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 8px;
        }

        /* --- BARRE DE PROGRESSION --- */
        .progress-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .progress-track {
            flex-grow: 1;
            height: 10px;
            background: #edf2f7;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), #fbbf24);
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .percent-text {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            width: 45px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* --- BOUTON ET ALERTES --- */
        .btn-refresh {
            width: 100%;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .btn-refresh:hover {
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(194, 120, 3, 0.3);
        }

        .status-card {
            background: #fdfaf1;
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-light);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .status-card p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--primary-hover);
        }

        /* Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .header { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; gap: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-info">
            <h1>R√©sultats du Scrutin</h1>
            <p>Mise √† jour automatique en temps r√©el</p>
        </div>
        <div class="total-badge">
            <span>Total des voix</span>
            <strong><%= @total_votes %></strong>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid-layout">
        <main class="main-content">
            <h2>üìä Classement d√©taill√©</h2>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Candidat</th>
                        <th style="text-align: center;">Voix</th>
                        <th>R√©partition</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% @candidates.sort_by(&:votes_count).reverse.each_with_index do |candidate, index| %>
                    <% percentage = @total_votes.zero? ? 0 : (candidate.votes_count.to_f / @total_votes * 100).round(1) %>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <div class="candidate-cell">
                                <span class="rank">#<%= index + 1 %></span>
                                <div>
                                    <span style="font-weight: 700;"><%= candidate.name %></span>
                                    <% if index == 0 %>
                                        <span class="leader-tag">LEADER</span>
                                    <% end %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                        <td style="text-align: center; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary);">
                            <%= candidate.votes_count %>
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            <div class="progress-container">
                                <div class="progress-track">
                                    <div class="progress-bar" style="width: <%= percentage %>%;"></div>
                                </div>
                                <span class="percent-text"><%= percentage %>%</span>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <% end %>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </main>

        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="sidebar-content">
                <button class="btn-refresh" onclick="window.location.reload()">
                    üîÑ Actualiser
                </button>
                <div class="status-card">
                    <h4 style="color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 5px; font-size: 0.9rem;">Statut du serveur</h4>
                    <p>Les donn√©es affich√©es sont certifi√©es conformes au registre centralis√© des votes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>